        "id": 2525451,
        "name": "Elliot Steele",
        "username": "Elliot_Steele",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/ec9cab/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-11-19T16:38:54.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>If memory serves me correctly I had the JL over the summer and it was in desperate need of air. A ton of VA upfront that was tough to get past but when it finally blew off and opened up it was singing. I\u2019d give it 2-3 hours of air if your bottle shows the same as mine did on the PnP. Love me some Kalin!</p>",
