      {
        "id": 2525993,
        "name": null,
        "username": "GZar",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/71e660/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-11-20T14:39:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"147421\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>The 1980 Kalin Cuv\u00e9e JL is a very rare bottle, where did you find it? Current release is 1999\u2026 1980 JL is a great wine and I have never encountered any VA, one of the best Kalin Pinot Noirs I have tasted in fact. The last bottle I had, I decanted and served which only did the wine good.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thanks, William.  I acquired 3 bottles from a local cellar with strong provenance\u2026I can only hope they provide the same experience as yours!  Good luck with your semi-new gig.</p>",
